{{companyName}} (hereafter: STM) requests {{supplierName}} (hereafter: Supplier) to submit a binding quotation for plumbing, sanitary, and HVAC works for the project:

{{projectName}}
Project number: {{projectNumber}}
Site address: {{siteAddress}}, {{siteZip}} {{siteCity}}

STM contact: {{stmContact}}
Supplier contact: {{supplierContact}}

The quotation shall be explicitly and exclusively based on the project documentation provided by STM, consisting of:
- the IFC model (if provided);
- the accompanying 2D drawings (PDF and/or DWG);
- this Request for Quotation document.

The Supplier shall not deviate from the specifications set out in this document without prior written approval from STM. Any deviation, assumption, or exclusion not explicitly stated in the Supplier's quotation shall be deemed accepted as specified herein.

The scope encompasses all materials, provisions, and logistics necessary for a complete and functional delivery. Items not explicitly excluded under Chapter 6 are deemed included.

STM reserves the right to award part of the scope to alternative suppliers.

Complete plumbing and sanitary:

Water supply: {{water}}
Fixtures: per room schedule
Hot water: {{hotW}}
Internal waste drainage: included
External connection: {{extConn}}

Heating: {{heating}}
Ventilation: {{vent}}
AHU: {{ahu}}

Per Bouwbesluit and NEN 1087.

Site: {{siteAddress}}, {{siteZip}} {{siteCity}}.

Working hours: {{workingHours}}
Estimated duration: {{duration}}
Start date: {{startDate}}

The Supplier shall:
- Mobilise within {{mobiliseDays}} working days after instruction
- Coordinate with STM site manager
- Maintain site cleanliness
- Reinstate any damage caused by Supplier's operations

Quantities indicative. STM may adjust +/- {{quantityTolerance}}% without price change per unit rate.
